===========

June 25 The Brian Setzer Orchestra led the opening of the Montreal Jazz Festival 2010, performing more than 150,000 people!
This Blu-ray disc captures the blistering 1 hour and 40 minutes set, which was easily one of the biggest shows of Brian ever! We guarantee this is one of the best rock shows I'll never see. That's saying a lot, but we mean it! "It's Gonna Rock, because that is what I do" has some amazing bonus and rare pictures that fans do not want to miss.
